headline.main: Justin Thomas Makes an Ace and Takes Lead in Mexico
headline.print_headline: Justin Thomas Makes an Ace and Takes Lead in Mexico

lead_paragraph: Justin Thomas hit a 6-iron that one-hopped into the bottom of the cup. Dustin Johnson hit a wedge that never came down from a tree. In one of the 10 fairways that Phil Mickelson missed, a spectator apparently ran off with his golf ball.
